**Deployment Environments:**

**1. Development:**
- Local machine
- Debug mode enabled
- Detailed error messages
- Hot reloading with nodemon
- Local database

```env
# .env.development
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/myapp_dev
JWT_SECRET=dev-secret
LOG_LEVEL=debug
```

**2. Staging:**
- Test server mirroring production
- Real services with test data
- QA testing environment
- Pre-production validation

```env
# .env.staging
NODE_ENV=staging
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster/myapp_staging
JWT_SECRET=staging-secret
LOG_LEVEL=info
```

**3. Production:**
- Live server with real users
- Optimized performance
- Security hardened
- Minimal error details exposed

```env
# .env.production
NODE_ENV=production
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster/myapp_prod
JWT_SECRET=super-secure-production-secret
LOG_LEVEL=warn
```

